snippet.title: Nick Cannon's Little Brother Javen Gets Flamed 😂 Wild 'N Out | #PleadTheFifth
snippet.description:
Javen tried to put Karlous Miller on the spot while he was in the hot seat during ‘Plead The Fifth’, but his shoes got in the way of his words. 😂
